review_data: Reviewed in the United States on March 10, 2021
name: Auntie Grizelda
title: Delish
review: The chocolate mint is amazing. It’s not too sweet or minty. It’s good either hot or cold. It’s not gritty, just a smooth drink.

name: Delaney Collins
title: Mint Chocolate Iced Coffee
review: I love everything about this! I blended up some milk with the powder and served it over ice! so yummy

review_data: Reviewed in the United States on October 15, 2020
name: Rose91
title: Delicious and subtle
review: The flavor is so lovely, you get the chocolatly taste without it being overbearing. The mint is really subtle and not in your face, more like an after taste, and it leaves your breath smelling deliciously. It's not one to give you warmth, or maybe it's just that I use it as an ice blend and haven't tried warm drinks, but I really enjoyed it.
